    %% Core orchestration
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| Dashboard
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| KServe
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| ModelMesh
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| ModelCtrl
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| DSPOp
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| NotebookCtrl
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| CodeFlare
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| KubeRay
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| Kueue
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| TrainingOp
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| TrustyAI
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| PrometheusStack
    RHODSOp -->|configures| ServiceMesh

    %% Dashboard dependencies
    Dashboard -->|proxies API| DSPOp
    Dashboard -->|proxies API| TrustyAI
    Dashboard -->|creates CRs| NotebookCtrl
    Dashboard -->|creates CRs| KServe

    %% KServe dependencies
    KServe -->|REQUIRED| Knative
    KServe -->|REQUIRED| Istio
    KServe -->|webhook certs| CertManager
    KServe -->|downloads models| S3
    KServe -->|downloads models| GCS
    KServe -->|downloads models| Azure

    %% ModelMesh dependencies
    ModelMesh -->|optional mTLS| Istio
    ModelMesh -->|downloads models| S3
    ModelMesh -->|metrics| PrometheusStack

    %% ODH Model Controller dependencies
    ModelCtrl -->|watches| KServe
    ModelCtrl -->|creates Routes| OpenShift
    ModelCtrl -->|creates VirtualServices| Istio
    ModelCtrl -->|creates AuthConfigs| Authorino
    ModelCtrl -->|creates ServiceMonitors| PrometheusStack

    %% Data Science Pipelines dependencies
    DSPOp -->|stores artifacts| S3
    DSPOp -->|metadata storage| ExtDB
    DSPOp -->|integrates| PrometheusStack

    %% Notebook Controller dependencies
    NotebookCtrl -->|creates Routes| OpenShift
    NotebookCtrl -->|OAuth integration| OpenShift
    NotebookCtrl -->|workbench images| Registry
    NotebookCtrl -->|runtime packages| PyPI
    NotebookCtrl -->|version control| Git

    %% CodeFlare dependencies
    CodeFlare -->|watches| KubeRay
    CodeFlare -->|integrates| Kueue
    CodeFlare -->|creates Routes| OpenShift
    CodeFlare -->|OAuth proxy| OpenShift

    %% KubeRay dependencies
    KubeRay -->|optional| Istio

    %% Kueue dependencies
    Kueue -->|watches jobs| TrainingOp
    Kueue -->|watches jobs| KubeRay
    Kueue -->|webhook certs| CertManager

    %% Training Operator dependencies
    TrainingOp -->|integrates| Kueue
    TrainingOp -->|saves checkpoints| S3
    TrainingOp -->|webhook certs| CertManager

    %% TrustyAI dependencies
    TrustyAI -->|patches| KServe
    TrustyAI -->|metrics| PrometheusStack
    TrustyAI -->|storage| ExtDB
    TrustyAI -->|creates Routes| OpenShift

    %% Platform-wide dependencies
    RHODSOp -->|manages resources| K8sAPI
    RHODSOp -->|fetches manifests| Git
    RHODSOp -->|OpenShift features| OpenShift

    Dashboard -->|authenticates| OpenShift
    KServe -->|API calls| K8sAPI
    ModelCtrl -->|API calls| K8sAPI
    DSPOp -->|API calls| K8sAPI
    NotebookCtrl -->|API calls| K8sAPI
    CodeFlare -->|API calls| K8sAPI
    KubeRay -->|API calls| K8sAPI
    Kueue -->|API calls| K8sAPI
    TrainingOp -->|API calls| K8sAPI
    TrustyAI -->|API calls| K8sAPI

    %% Monitoring
    PrometheusStack -->|scrapes metrics| KServe
    PrometheusStack -->|scrapes metrics| ModelMesh
    PrometheusStack -->|scrapes metrics| DSPOp
    PrometheusStack -->|scrapes metrics| TrustyAI
    PrometheusStack -->|scrapes metrics| TrainingOp
    PrometheusStack -->|scrapes metrics| Kueue

    %% Service Mesh
    ServiceMesh -->|mTLS| KServe
    ServiceMesh -->|mTLS| DSPOp
    ServiceMesh -->|mTLS| TrustyAI

